{"tid":2119080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅芯口罩供應商子公司列美黑名單","createTime":"2020-07-22T01:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T02:29:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e57d79b8ecfccf4d0ef2ebb1b891aa42efec2743","tid":2119080,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/NYGCT75JXRRZWDAITSRORZFI6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FNYGCT75JXRRZWDAITSRORZFI6I%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=04ecedfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200722%2FNYGCT75JXRRZWDAITSRORZFI6I%2F&h=2a9677b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200722/NYGCT75JXRRZWDAITSRORZFI6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銅芯口罩供應商子公司列美黑名單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有「棉花公主」稱號的溢達集團董事長楊敏德捲入中美角力的暴風眼。美國指包括昌吉溢德在內的11間中國企業，協助中共侵犯新疆少數族裔的人權，將他們列入新一波制裁黑名單內，當中被指涉及強制勞動的昌吉溢達，母公司溢達集團為港府「銅芯抗疫口罩」供應貼面紗布。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東盟視像會議 京官斥美煽動抗中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jX1IcP8xeGyqUYkVSdupoIFki64=/640x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WCPILRJNKDLEEJ2IMCD6AQEWIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjX1IcP8xeGyqUYkVSdupoIFki64%3D%2F640x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWCPILRJNKDLEEJ2IMCD6AQEWIY.jpg&h=eb6050ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溢達紡織被美國制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉助中共侵維族人權<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部美東時間周一公佈新一波制裁名單，指11間華企涉在新。。。。。。。。。。。。。。溢達集團為港府「銅芯抗疫口罩」供應貼面紗布，外界關注該批紗布是否源自昌吉溢達。<br />\n<br />\n至於被指利用基因分析協助打壓的兩間基因科技公司，其母公司「華大基因」旗下華昇診斷中心獲港府邀請進行武肺病毒檢測。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n溢達集團行政總裁車克燾周一。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華大基因表示，。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"953cc2bad893ef40ff65a1085a5dd00dcbbfdb0a","tid":2119080,"uid":24788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"邊個戴=支持集中營"},{"pid":"d2468caadaee5876274d5025853b4b16682e16b2","tid":2119080,"uid":257272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔係啵...根據基本法...."},{"pid":"dbccdc31c4b35f4cfc0ee220b2b1a25eea06a49d","tid":2119080,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a220d700ee97443ab0b1f93b06531bf24fabb9a3","tid":2119080,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a32a1ff2069980643fde0c78140dfbe3afc5dd9","tid":2119080,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYwBujs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYwBujs.gif&h=1d55b1b8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}